label-about: OUR COMPANY DESIGNED THE BEST HOME AND INTERIOR
title-about: We know that good design means good business
text-about: Founded by Founder Luong Hoang Linh in 2017, we’re an employee-owned firm pursuing a democratic design process that values everyone’s input. Today we have more than 150 people in Da Nang providing architecture, interior & urban design services from concept to completion.
prize3: We recruited about 10 members for my company. Since that, we worked and helped together.
prize4: We built and designed for more over 1000 peoples.
prize5: We are recognized as a famous design company at DaNang City.
